- No way!

05:41.842 --> 05:43.469
(Groaning)

05:45.262 --> 05:47.306
<i>It's not enough. It won't work.</i>

05:47.431 --> 05:49.224
<i>These guys don't trust anyone!</i>

05:49.350 --> 05:51.310
- Have you got a better idea?

05:51.727 --> 05:52.728
<i>- I think so.</i>

05:53.395 --> 05:56.899
<i>Put your guns on the ground,
or he's dead! Now!</i>

05:57.024 --> 05:58.901
- Put your guns down. Do what he says.

05:59.360 --> 06:01.653
<i>- Guns on the ground!</i>
- Put your guns down!

06:02.571 --> 06:06.241
<i>- You, get over there!
I don't want anyone behind me!</i>

06:06.367 --> 06:10.120
<i>Nobody behind me! Got it?</i>
(Martin, over radio): Put your guns down.

06:10.245 --> 06:12.664
<i>- Lower your guns!
Get that fucking gun down!</i>

06:12.790 --> 06:14.416
- He's one of us.
<i>- Away from the truck!</i>

06:14.541 --> 06:17.127
- I repeat, he's one of us.
<i>- I said no one behind me!</i>

06:17.252 --> 06:18.629
- Put your guns down!

06:19.713 --> 06:21.423
<i>- I want to see hands!</i>

06:22.883 --> 06:23.926
<i>You drive!</i>

06:34.395 --> 06:37.981
<i>- Fuck de shit de calice
de fuckin' tabarnak!</i>

06:38.107 --> 06:39.942
<i>- Your French isn't rusty at all!</i>

06:40.067 --> 06:42.736
- How come the guys
who run the show weren't there?

06:43.404 --> 06:44.947
<i>- Who tipped you off?</i>

06:45.072 --> 06:49.118
- An informant who we flipped after he tried
to sell a hot car to one of my agents.

06:49.243 --> 06:50.327
- Well, he played you!

06:50.452 --> 06:52.830
<i>DiPietro and Dubois never go there.</i>

06:52.955 --> 06:56.291
<i>All they do there is deactivate
the cars' GPS and alarm systems</i>

06:56.417 --> 06:58.460
<i>before sending them
to the main garage.</i>

06:58.585 --> 07:01.755
- OK, you don't have to go back.
We just need to find DiPietro.

07:01.880 --> 07:04.466
With what we've got on him collectively,
he's done!

07:04.591 --> 07:06.760
<i>- No, there's something bigger going on!</i>

07:06.885 --> 07:09.471
<i>I'm sure of it.
I've been on them for a year.</i>

07:09.596 --> 07:12.599
<i>We can go at them harder,
but I have to go back in.</i>

07:13.267 --> 07:17.312
- OK. But if I get a hinky feeling...
- Whatever you do, don't itch it.

07:17.438 --> 07:21.191
- I will call it off, I promise you,
if you disobey a single one of my orders.

07:22.192 --> 07:24.319
- Your... your orders?

07:24.445 --> 07:26.822
- Mm-hmm.
(Laughing)

07:26.947 --> 07:30.033
- No, no, no, no! No, no. No.

07:30.159 --> 07:32.995
<i>I'm not working for you,
I'm working with you.</i>

07:33.120 --> 07:36.039
- Provincial, federal.

07:36.707 --> 07:38.500
My investigation trumps yours.

07:38.625 --> 07:42.004
If you don't like it, you can leave.
I'll find DiPietro myself.

07:42.129 --> 07:44.173
And you can return
grovelling to your boss

07:44.298 --> 07:46.967
