a year of taxpayers' money.

07:52.931 --> 07:54.516
- You've changed, man!

07:54.641 --> 07:56.101
- Thank you!

07:56.685 --> 07:59.354
Now let's get going.
I've got a tracker on me.

07:59.480 --> 08:02.900
My men will be here any minute.
How do we get you back in?

08:03.025 --> 08:04.943
