08:32.929 --> 08:33.889
- Nope.

08:36.808 --> 08:39.394
<i>It'll still work.</i>

08:39.520 --> 08:43.941
<i>OK, we'll say that you disarmed me,
we fought,</i>

08:44.066 --> 08:47.152
<i>you lost control of the vehicle
and I got away.</i>

08:47.277 --> 08:49.905
<i>It has to look real, though,</i>

08:50.030 --> 08:52.616
<i>as if the airbag went off in your face.</i>

08:52.741 --> 08:55.953
- OK. How exactly do you imagine that--
Oh fuck!

08:56.078 --> 08:57.371
