08:57.496 --> 08:58.872
- You OK?

08:58.997 --> 09:01.833
Sorry, man. Show me.

09:05.212 --> 09:06.088
<i>That's good!</i>

09:07.839 --> 09:09.508
<i>That'll work!</i>

09:10.092 --> 09:12.928
<i>- You haven't changed at all.</i>

09:13.053 --> 09:14.930
