11:57.634 --> 11:59.720
<i>- I'm taking you to the hospital!
- No!</i>

11:59.845 --> 12:02.139
<i>- Get me the first-aid kit!
- No!</i>

12:02.264 --> 12:05.392
<i>They have to think I spent
