<i>- Last night,
during a police raid</i>

13:44.866 --> 13:48.495
<i>of a known Italian crime boss's
garage of stolen cars,</i>

13:48.620 --> 13:50.914
<i>a police officer was taken hostage</i>

13:51.039 --> 13:53.875
<i>by one of the scumbags
that he was trying to arrest.</i>

13:54.000 --> 13:56.920
<i>He's with us this morning.
Perhaps he has something to say this morning.</i>

13:57.420 --> 13:59.464
<i>Mr. Ward, Poirier, Claude.</i>

13:59.589 --> 14:02.425
<i>How did a low-level scumbag</i>

14:02.551 --> 14:06.179
<i>manage to kidnap a highly trained officer
like yourself?</i>

14:07.138 --> 14:08.723
- Uh...

14:08.849 --> 14:12.018
<i>When we entered the garage,</i>

14:12.143 --> 14:17.440
<i>we were surprised
by the pushback we encountered.</i>

14:17.566 --> 14:19.985
<i>Many of them were armed.</i>

14:20.110 --> 14:23.572
<i>- Didn't they teach you how to deal with that
at the Ontarian Nicolet,</i>

14:23.697 --> 14:26.950
<i>that sometimes criminals might be armed?</i>

14:27.075 --> 14:29.077
- Uh, well...

14:29.911 --> 14:33.456
<i>I'm sorry, but I don't know...
Who's Nicolet?</i>

14:33.582 --> 14:36.751
- Nicolet is the Quebec police school.

14:36.877 --> 14:39.337
<i>Do you want me
to "conti-news" in English?</i>

14:39.462 --> 14:40.672
<i>- No, that's all right!</i>

14:40.797 --> 14:45.093
<i>But could you please speak
a little more slowly?</i>

14:46.720 --> 14:49.014
<i>- Is this my stag party?</i>

14:52.100 --> 14:53.435
- Where the fuck were you?

14:53.560 --> 14:55.145
