01:48:17.200 --> 01:48:18.784
- Goddammit!

01:48:18.910 --> 01:48:20.036
MC!

01:48:20.161 --> 01:48:21.204
<i>- I'm listening.</i>

01:48:21.329 --> 01:48:22.413
