<i>- I don't give a shit!</i>

01:49:45.580 --> 01:49:46.747
<i>- Ayoye!</i>

01:49:50.459 --> 01:49:55.423
<i>- You asshole! This is going on YouTube, pig!</i>

01:49:56.215 --> 01:49:58.384
