01:50:55.149 --> 01:50:58.944
<i>You want to drive into the river?
Fine! Let's drive into the river!</i>

01:51:01.238 --> 01:51:03.282
- Get out of the way!

01:51:03.407 --> 01:51:06.369
Get out of the fucking way!

01:51:06.494 --> 01:51:08.746
Jesus, David!

01:51:08.871 --> 01:51:10.206
- Oh shit!

01:51:25.763 --> 01:51:29.558
- You fucking hot dog, teenager,

01:51:29.684 --> 01:51:33.229
shit-disturbing Quebecois
de fucking <i>tête de cochon</i>

01:51:33.354 --> 01:51:34.897
<i>de tabernak!</i>

01:51:35.022 --> 01:51:37.483
<i>- Your French is coming along great!</i>

01:51:37.608 --> 01:51:39.610
<i>Immersion really works!</i>

01:51:43.614 --> 01:51:46.742
<i>I'm sure the computer system is down now!</i>

01:51:47.827 --> 01:51:50.246
