<i>I'll meet you there. We'll split the plane ticket.</i>

01:52:15.688 --> 01:52:16.605
Deal?

01:52:16.731 --> 01:52:17.982
- Deal.

01:52:18.107 --> 01:52:20.067
- OK.
- Right there.

01:52:21.110 --> 01:52:22.236
(Grunting)

01:52:25.114 --> 01:52:27.366
(Panting)

01:52:29.535 --> 01:52:30.995
Fuck!

