01:56:14.635 --> 01:56:17.429
- Everything's going to be OK, son.

01:56:17.554 --> 01:56:21.517
- I'm sorry, Dad. I'm so sorry.

01:56:23.477 --> 01:56:24.853
- Just start walking.

01:56:27.064 --> 01:56:28.524
